{"tid":328543,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[FM2017] 史篤城前四之路...","createTime":"2017-07-19T16:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T06:05:33.000Z","uid":72034,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0cac6f66b675501151e8c3ec1575a324da4e091e","tid":328543,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"之前睇到其他post,搞到自己都想出埋一份,加上呢排實在太得閒,所以未來幾日應該會不停更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大約玩左FM兩年,唔算好勁,戰術都唔會太深入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解會用史篤城? 因為呢隊算係英超中遊,降班又冇份但又打唔到歐洲賽,加上呢幾年開始唔打傳統英式足球改為技術型打法,所以想試下用佢主打控球小組滲入,睇下有冇機會入到歐霸,更進一步既就想入前四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外就係會用繁中,因為一黎方便,二黎其他佢都譯得幾好笑,而且比賽只會打一次,輸就輸唔會重打<br />\n<br />\n入正題,開檔我創左個叫Xavi既manager<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.brain4.photobox.com/54311886eb3b546823328e673246e1f66c972a12dd687022bd176c0136b06d8d31689b35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.brain4.photobox.com%2F54311886eb3b546823328e673246e1f66c972a12dd687022bd176c0136b06d8d31689b35.jpg&h=6d8f8e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開季係英超第一場既前一個星期左右,即係冇打友誼賽熟習戰術,同埋冇乜時間去買人<br />\n<br />\n戰術方面,當然係控球,而且仲係好執著果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,陣式係4-3-3,單防中兩個中場中,右翼位會入中路,邊路就比哂右邊後衛會插上, 左翼就會拉邊傳中<br />\n一般程度逼搶,心態暫時係用住標準,遲D季中可能會變<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/234458_678c31e8b371bddc10ee6439d9839e84.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F234458_678c31e8b371bddc10ee6439d9839e84.PNG&h=951a1102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/234516_7f3d58b193ac4ce8e0730da9d0d6e8ce.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F234516_7f3d58b193ac4ce8e0730da9d0d6e8ce.PNG&h=8dfea939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題來了,原來得百幾萬轉會費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,想買人都買唔到,好在助教推薦左D人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/234921_4517285d30d12c978510261c986ec773.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F234921_4517285d30d12c978510261c986ec773.PNG&h=91363b3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/234936_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F234936_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=6a4eb0b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗講咁多,即簽Lassana Diarra,打防中都OK<br />\n免簽多個教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,因為原本都幾廢下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/235808_9eb9cd58b9ea5e04c890326b5c1f471f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F235808_9eb9cd58b9ea5e04c890326b5c1f471f.png&h=c10ef1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/235348_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F235348_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png&h=e7b5e50d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傷兵名單<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/235450_1143466cf97b9544ce55de4623a85e84.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F235450_1143466cf97b9544ce55de4623a85e84.PNG&h=e9efac23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n神射手賠率<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/235519_a9f6262884ffa5617d8922a24e28151f.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F235519_a9f6262884ffa5617d8922a24e28151f.PNG&h=02c26836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下場對手會係屈福特<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/235714_6a5c402c4989c42a94a39be08baad337.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F235714_6a5c402c4989c42a94a39be08baad337.PNG&h=6975bd43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一陣再更新<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0faab310c5518813da5e9e52a9733e8950004a48","tid":328543,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:17:33.000Z","msg":"屈福特今場波係用5-3-2,應該就係打反撃為主<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/001247_7b6fbd4c592d356e087a0f1053751007.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F001247_7b6fbd4c592d356e087a0f1053751007.png&h=5506b5f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賽前對手公開話我太年輕,未夠班做manager<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/001013_01effdac6062831623d62c08febfb1df.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F001013_01effdac6062831623d62c08febfb1df.PNG&h=78337a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我決定比D顏色佢對波睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/001405_5a5e1e6dfb102b4c8eb563c419eb715a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F001405_5a5e1e6dfb102b4c8eb563c419eb715a.png&h=32218e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落埋order下下出腳<br />\n<br />\n今場正選陣容<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/001543_f20faae54c292bdbe2bb358a00854f62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F001543_f20faae54c292bdbe2bb358a00854f62.png&h=7ff10ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於出左order但球員未accept,所以都係用返原班人馬"},{"pid":"e2585b3bb1713db850d34477bd83a9cf96bad025","tid":328543,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7067a13c9e8ba1ca2cc4fd74b2e465d7d4d06d3","tid":328543,"uid":72034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"一開波都係我地控黎黎踢,屈福特主要都係守住,隻方都冇乜到肉攻勢,間中打幾下遠射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到左三十一分鐘,終於打破悶局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l1KUreytG8aS7Msk8/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl1KUreytG8aS7Msk8%2Fgiphy.gif&h=4e9c0680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙基利招牌左腳,勁抽遠上角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過左幾分鐘差D再入,好在對方解圍<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l1CC3rgpw2v9WDcQM/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl1CC3rgpw2v9WDcQM%2Fgiphy.gif&h=5be29d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁半場就一球領先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n半場數據<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/003058_e9c8b336d53f38d7cad01cbe8e5d6497.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F003058_e9c8b336d53f38d7cad01cbe8e5d6497.PNG&h=8208fd75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下半場一出黎就故意放慢節奏,慢慢踢,對方都唔諗住攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地仲差D入多球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可惜射中人<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oge8hq1HPAQQEVUoo/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oge8hq1HPAQQEVUoo%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e44b6c26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n領先一球永遠好危險,到左70絃分鐘仲係1-0,所以轉陣4-1-4-1,沙基利打返左中場,Berahino冇刎作用換入防守型前鋒Diouf,右中場換走Arnautovic,換入Walters加強防守,可惜冇CAP圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n臨完場差D含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l1CC6AyTNaF8boSVG/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl1CC6AyTNaF8boSVG%2Fgiphy.gif&h=8685c1b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果都係1-0守到完場<br />\n全場數據<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/004132_1d1361a011918c7195cddb7e2c31ba78.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F004132_1d1361a011918c7195cddb7e2c31ba78.PNG&h=66931bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今場到肉攻勢唔多,主要係冇創造力,但得百幾萬轉會費下,買入好球員係無可能,唯有靠訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStoke city 1-0 Watford <br />\n(Shaqiri,32)"},{"pid":"73e33f44fab0bd90436a0cda381d47ad6baa26ea","tid":328543,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:48:25.000Z","msg":"聽日再更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f269e4683dbd5c9cf426e799eba0e0192d47df","tid":328543,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:47:54.000Z","msg":"有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea38fce6d013c4a429b2f3d8481f89b47146cb3c","tid":328543,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:53:30.000Z","msg":"屌你咩出一場就第日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1950b97f450d49f379df01ce0cb5cdb1676d0a7e","tid":328543,"uid":115186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:03:50.000Z","msg":"邊度有繁中down <br />\n三個月冇玩，之前用垃圾殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582a6e4079fa64e38bdf420fd98662cc3aab0443","tid":328543,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度有繁中down <br />\n三個月冇玩，之前用垃圾殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n官方更新咗出咗正體版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd4c5b3eb9f748154b3f81aac752d1993c9e0a9","tid":328543,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊度有繁中down <br />\n三個月冇玩，之前用垃圾殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n官方更新咗出咗正體版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以開返黎玩"},{"pid":"5112b85b5ef6a032259643f3406fbb9aea9c1b37","tid":328543,"uid":57227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:29:50.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2a94762d8ede703270668286983db61c6e132883","tid":328543,"uid":43861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:54:36.000Z","msg":"覺得電腦好煩轉左玩手機版"},{"pid":"6507fb92a4fd798e03e9ddc537d93ebab66fe912","tid":328543,"uid":59942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}